author: Associated Press
title: Blue Jays belt three homers in Game 3 win over Royals
text:
Photo: Matt Slocum, Associated Press Kansas City Royals' Alcides Escobar celebrates in the dugout after scoring against the Toronto Blue Jays during the first inning in Game 3 of baseball's American League Championship Series on Monday, Oct. 19, 2015, in Toronto. (AP Photo/Matt Slocum) Kansas City Royals' Alcides Escobar celebrates in the dugout after...
TORONTO — The Toronto Blue Jays were eager to get home after dropping the first two games of the AL Championship Series in Kansas City.
